The paper discusses the use of machine learning for malware detection, specifically ransomware, and evaluates the resiliency of ML algorithms for security. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the need for defense improvement in ML-based approaches, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SI).
